      <text x="200" y="1175" font-family="'Plus Jakarta Sans', 'Outfit', sans-serif" font-weight="800" font-size="14" fill="#ffb703" letter-spacing="3" text-anchor="middle">SNAPVIBE ✦ MEMORIES</text>
